<%- include('../../partials/layout/top.ejs'); %>

<div class="request-page">
  <div class="grid-container fluid">
    <div class="grid-container grid-x grid-margin-x" style="margin:auto;">
      <div class='cell small-12 medium-12 large-12'>
        <h1>May 2021 Commencement RSVP</h1>

        <% if(commencement){%>
          <% 
          //Vars 
          const validDate = moment().isBetween(moment(new Date(commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'OpenDate')['value'])).utc().utcOffset(-5),moment(new Date(commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'DueDate')['value'])).utc().utcOffset(-5))
          %>
          <% //Check Date is Valid 
          if(validDate){%>
            <input id="status" type="hidden" style="display:none" value="<%= commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Status')['value']%>">
            <input id="busObRecId" type="hidden" style="display:none" value="<%-commencement.busObRecId%>">
            <input id="busObPublicId" type="hidden" style="display:none" value="<%-commencement.busObPublicId%>">
            <input id="multipleCeremonies" type="hidden" style="display:none" value="<%-commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'MultipleCeremonies')['value']%>">
          <div class="grid-container grid-x grid-margin-x align-center" style="margin:auto;">
            <div class='cell small-12 medium-4 large-3 hide-for-small-only'>
              <% if (locals.user && user.id && locals.userAttributes) { %>

                  <div class="user-info" style="text-align: center;">
                    <div class="profile-img-square" style="background-image:url('/img/ico-intro.svg');"></div>
                    <p id="verified"><i class="far fa-badge-check color-bright-2"></i> Verified User</p>
                      <p id="full-name"><%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'FirstName')['value']%> <%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'LastName')['value']%></p>
                      <p id="wpi-id"><%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'WPIID')['value']%></p>
                      <p id="wpi-email"><i class="fas fa-envelope-square"></i> <%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'WPIEmail')['value']%></p>
                  </div>
              <% } %>

            </div>
            <div class='cell  small-12 medium-10 large-9'>
            <div class="help-form" id="terms" style="<%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Status')['value'] == 'Completed' ? "display:none" : ""%>">
              <p><strong><%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'FirstName')['value']%>,</strong><br> This form is used to indicate your attendance at 2021 WPI Commencement. Completion of this form is required in order for you to attend Commencement. No walk-in attendance at Commencement is permitted. <strong>Responses are due no later than April 12, 2021</strong>.</p>
              <p>Please review the following information before submitting your response:</p>
              <ul class="card-list">
                <li><span><i style="color:var(--color-bright-5);"class="fad fa-info-circle"></i></span><span>Your assigned ceremony may not be changed.<br>Students earning both bachelor's <em>and</em> master's degrees in 2021 are permitted to attend the ceremony for each degree.<br>Ceremonies will be held outdoors on the WPI Quad, rain or shine.</span></li>
                <li><span><i style="color:var(--color-bright-3);"class="fad fa-laptop-house"></i></span><span>Graduates who are unable to attend their assigned in-person ceremony have the option to participate in a virtual Commencement ceremony on Saturday, May 22 at 10:00 a.m. Eastern time.</span></li>
                <li><span><i style="color:var(--color-pop);"class="fad fa-user-graduate"></i></span><span>If you are attending Commencement in person, regalia (cap & gown) is required.<br> <strong>The deadline for ordering regalia is April 9, 2021</strong> – <a href="https://www.buildagrad.com/wpi" target="_blank">order here</a>. <br><em>No regalia will be available for purchase on the day of Commencement ceremonies</em>. <br>Virtual Commencement attendees are not required to purchase regalia but may do so if they wish.</span></li>
                <li><span><i style="color:var(--color-bright-1);"class="fad fa-user-friends"></i></span><span>Each graduate is permitted up to two guests. <br>All guests must register in advance, have a ticket for entry to the ceremony, and attest to health and safety protocols. <br><strong>Additional information about guest tickets will be sent to your WPI email address in mid-April</strong>.</span></li>
                <li><span><i style="color:var(--color-bright-4);"class="fad fa-tv-retro"></i></span><span>Family and friends unable to attend may watch Commencement the livestream on the web.</span></li>
                <li><span><i style="color:var(--color-bright-2);"class="fad fa-shield-virus"></i></span><span>Compliance with all WPI and Massachusetts travel advisories, health and safety protocols, and other COVID-19 guidelines is required by all graduates and guests.</span></li>
              </ul>
              <button id="button-continue"style="margin: 0 auto;max-width: 60%;display: block;" class="button-submit">Agree and Continue to Form <i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-right"></i></button>

            </div>

            <div class="help-form" id="commenceForm" style="<%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Status')['value'] != 'Completed' ? "display:none" : ""%>">
              
              <% if(commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1')['value'] != ""){%>
              <fieldset>
                <legend>Ceremony <%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1')['value']%> - <%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1Title')['value']%></legend>
              <h3 style="margin-bottom:0;font-weight: 600;font-size: .875rem;">Choose an attendance option for Ceremony <%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1')['value']%>:</h3>
                <div class='grid-x grid-margin-x impact-boxes'>

                  <div class="cell small-12 medium-12">
                    <input type="radio" id="commence1-choice-yes" name="commence1Choice" value="I will attend this ceremony in person" <%= commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1Response')['value'] == "I will attend this ceremony in person" ? "Checked" : ""%>>
                    <label for="commence1-choice-yes">I will attend Ceremony <%=commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1')['value']%> in person on <%=moment(new Date(commencement.fields.find(f => f.name === 'Ceremony1Date')['value'])).utc().utcOffset(-5).format('dddd, MMMM Do YYYY, h:mm a')%></label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="cell small-12 medium-12">
